"{\"abstract\":\"We propose a joint formulation for learning task-specific cross-lingual word embeddings, along with classifiers for that task. Unlike prior work, which first learns the embeddings from parallel data and then plugs them in a supervised learning problem, our approach is oneshot: a single optimization problem combines a co-regularizer for the multilingual embeddings with a task-specific loss. We present theoretical results showing the limitation of Euclidean co-regularizers to increase the embedding dimension, a limitation which does not exist for other co-regularizers (such as the \\u20181distance). Despite its simplicity, our method achieves state-of-the-art accuracies on the RCV1/RCV2 dataset when transferring from English to German, with training times below 1 minute. On the TED Corpus, we obtain the highest reported scores on 10 out of 11 languages.\",\"arxivId\":null,\"authors\":[{\"authorId\":\"145250231\",\"name\":\"Daniel C. Ferreira\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/145250231\"},{\"authorId\":\"145644643\",\"name\":\"Andr\\u00e9 F. T. Martins\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/145644643\"},{\"authorId\":\"97946526\",\"name\":\"Mariana S. C. Almeida\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/97946526\"}],\"citationVelocity\":0,\"citations\":[{\"arxivId\":null,\"authors\":[{\"authorId\":\"73773451\",\"name\":\"Patricia Chiril\"},{\"authorId\":\"3350632\",\"name\":\"F. Benamara\"},{\"authorId\":\"2975481\",\"name\":\"V\\u00e9ronique Moriceau\"},{\"authorId\":\"1405812468\",\"name\":\"M. Coulomb-Gully\"},{\"authorId\":\"50333254\",\"name\":\"Abhishek Kumar\"},{\"authorId\":\"70045636\",\"name\":\"E. Macron\"}],\"doi\":null,\"intent\":[],\"isInfluential\":false,\"paperId\":\"f303af3b8fa8f6a50fe5b19afa605b8908acd3b0\",\"title\":\"Multilingual and Multitarget Hate Speech Detection in Tweets\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/f303af3b8fa8f6a50fe5b19afa605b8908acd3b0\",\"venue\":\"PFIA\",\"year\"